## Project [/projects/{id}]
A single Project object.

The Project resource has the following attributes: 

- id
- name
- location
- description
- touched
- created
- modified

+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Project to perform action with. Has example value.

### Retrieve a Project [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header

            X-My-Header: The Value

    + Body

            { "id": 1, "name": "PasMan", "location": "http://pasman.io", "description": "PasMan is a fast and easy to use service to manage passwords.", "touched": "1405888671", "created": "1405888671", "modified": "1405888671" }

### Remove a Project [DELETE]
+ Response 204

