## Identity [/identities/{id}]
A single Indentity object.

The Indentity resource has the following attributes:

- id
- project_id
- server
- path
- user
- pass
- memo
- tags
- touched
- created
- modified

+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Identity to perform action with. Has example value.

### Retrieve an Identity [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            { "id": 1, "project_id": "1", "server": "http://pasman.io", "path": "/admin", "user": "batman", "pass": "3KDhcave", "memo": "Pass rotated every 3m", "tags": [1], "touched": "1405888671", "created": "1405888671", "modified": "1405888671" }

### Remove an Identity [DELETE]
+ Response 204

